Package: siduction-art-gnome-xmas
Architecture: all
Provides: siduction-art-gnome-theme
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 siduction-art-wallpaper-xmas,
 siduction-icons,
Recommends: dmz-cursor-theme
Description: Gnome theme for the siduction 12-2.0 release
 release specific metapackage depending on icons and wallpapers to be
 used in combination with the Gnome Desktop Environment.
 .
 Gnome artwork metapackage for: siduction 12-2.0 (Xmas-2012)

Package: siduction-art-kde-xmas
Architecture: all
Provides: siduction-art-kde-theme
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 siduction-art-ksplash-xmas,
 siduction-art-kdm-xmas,
 siduction-art-wallpaper-xmas,
 siduction-icons,
Recommends: dmz-cursor-theme
Description: KDE theme for the siduction 12-2.0 release
 release specific metapackage depending on ksplash, kdm and KDE themes to be
 used in combination with the K Desktop Environment. This package also
 provides a release specific color scheme for KDE.
 .
 KDE artwork metapackage for: siduction 12-2.0 (Xmas-2012)

Package: siduction-art-kdm-xmas
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
		 kdm
Description: KDM theme for the siduction 12-2.0 release
 release specific artwork theme for the KDM display manager to be used in
 combination with the K Desktop Environment.
 .
 KDM artwork for: siduction 12-2.0 (Xmas-2012)
 .
 This package does not override existing theme configurations and needs to be
 selected manually.

Package: siduction-art-ksplash-xmas
